The other two out of four exhibit dogs stolen from a motel in Bellflower were found, Los Angeles County Sheriffs announced on Thursday.
The four show dogs - two Akitas and two Welsh Pembroke Corgis - went missing Tuesday when someone stole the Chevrolet Express van in which they had spent the night outside a Bellflower Motel 6, authorities said.
